---
import BaseLayout from '../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Start Here"
  description="New to Editorial Intelligence? Your orientation guide to the ecosystem, the frameworks, and where to begin."
>

  <!-- ── Hero ── -->
  <section class="sh-hero container-site">
    <div class="sh-hero-inner">
      <span class="sh-time-badge">About 10 minutes</span>
      <h1 class="sh-h1">New to Editorial Intelligence?</h1>
      <p class="sh-sub">Everything you need to understand Editorial Intelligence, how it works, and where to begin.</p>
      <p class="sh-support">Whether you're a content leader, marketer, researcher, product team or simply curious about the future of editorial, this page will help you navigate the site.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="sh-rule container-site" />

  <!-- ── Section 1: Choose your path ── -->
  <section class="sh-section container-site">
    <p class="sh-eyebrow">Choose your path</p>
    <div class="sh-path-grid">

      <a href="/guide" class="sh-path-card group">
        <span class="sh-path-icon">👋</span>
        <div>
          <p class="sh-path-title">I'm new</p>
          <p class="sh-path-desc">I'm discovering Editorial Intelligence for the first time.</p>
          <div class="sh-path-links">
            <span class="sh-path-cta">Read the Guide →</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <div class="sh-path-card">
        <span class="sh-path-icon">🏢</span>
        <div>
          <p class="sh-path-title">I lead a team</p>
          <p class="sh-path-desc">I want to understand how Editorial Intelligence can improve research, content, thought leadership and organisational knowledge.</p>
          <div class="sh-path-links">
            <a href="/editorial-intelligence-os" class="sh-path-cta">Explore Editorial Intelligence OS →</a>
            <a href="/applications" class="sh-path-link">Applications</a>
            <a href="/frameworks" class="sh-path-link">Frameworks</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sh-path-card">
        <span class="sh-path-icon">🤝</span>
        <div>
          <p class="sh-path-title">I need help</p>
          <p class="sh-path-desc">I want help improving my organisation's visibility, editorial capability or strategic content.</p>
          <div class="sh-path-links">
            <a href="/work" class="sh-path-cta">See Consulting →</a>
            <a href="/work/ai-visibility-audit" class="sh-path-link">AI Visibility Audit</a>
            <a href="/work" class="sh-path-link">Work With Me</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="sh-rule container-site" />

  <!-- ── Section 2: What is Editorial Intelligence ── -->
  <section class="sh-section container-site">
    <div class="sh-what-grid">
      <div>
        <p class="sh-eyebrow">The discipline</p>
        <h2 class="sh-h2">What is Editorial Intelligence?</h2>
        <div class="sh-what-body">
          <p>Editorial Intelligence is the discipline of turning organisational knowledge into connected narratives, reusable systems and strategic editorial assets.</p>
          <p>Rather than producing more content, it helps organisations make better use of the knowledge they already possess.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/intelligence" class="sh-btn">Learn the discipline →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="sh-what-stat-col">
        <div class="sh-stat-card">
          <p class="sh-stat-number">80%</p>
          <p class="sh-stat-label">of organisational knowledge goes unused after the project that created it ends</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-stat-card">
          <p class="sh-stat-number">3×</p>
          <p class="sh-stat-label">more narrative surfaces from evidence when it is connected rather than published and archived</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="sh-rule container-site" />

  <!-- ── Section 3: Why now ── -->
  <section class="sh-section container-site">
    <p class="sh-eyebrow">Why now</p>
    <h2 class="sh-h2">The conditions have changed</h2>
    <div class="sh-why-grid">

      <div class="sh-why-card">
        <div class="sh-why-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 3v18M3 12h18" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="sh-why-text">AI made creating content dramatically cheaper.</p>
        <p class="sh-why-sub">Production is no longer the bottleneck. Deciding what deserves to exist — and connecting it into a position — is.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="sh-why-card">
        <div class="sh-why-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M3 6h18M3 12h12M3 18h8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="sh-why-text">Most organisations already possess more insight than they know how to use.</p>
        <p class="sh-why-sub">Research, customer evidence, events and internal expertise sit in silos. The synthesis gap is the real problem.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="sh-why-card">
        <div class="sh-why-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M3 17l6-6 4 4 8-8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="sh-why-text">The competitive advantage is no longer publishing more. It's organising knowledge better.</p>
        <p class="sh-why-sub">AI systems form their picture of what you are credible about from consistent, evidence-backed positions — not from volume.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="sh-rule container-site" />

  <!-- ── Section 4: How everything fits ── -->
  <section class="sh-section container-site">
    <p class="sh-eyebrow">The architecture</p>
    <h2 class="sh-h2">How everything fits together</h2>
    <p class="sh-section-desc">Each level builds on the one above it. Click any level to explore.</p>
    <div class="sh-roadmap">

      <a href="/intelligence" class="sh-roadmap-node sh-roadmap-node--top">
        <span class="sh-roadmap-label">Editorial Intelligence</span>
        <span class="sh-roadmap-sub">The discipline and guiding principles</span>
      </a>
      <div class="sh-roadmap-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</div>

      <a href="/frameworks/evidence-engine" class="sh-roadmap-node">
        <span class="sh-roadmap-label">Evidence Engine</span>
        <span class="sh-roadmap-sub">The infrastructure that captures and connects signals</span>
      </a>
      <div class="sh-roadmap-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</div>

      <a href="/cycle" class="sh-roadmap-node">
        <span class="sh-roadmap-label">Editorial Intelligence Cycle</span>
        <span class="sh-roadmap-sub">The operating model that turns evidence into action</span>
      </a>
      <div class="sh-roadmap-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</div>

      <a href="/editorial-intelligence-os" class="sh-roadmap-node">
        <span class="sh-roadmap-label">Editorial Intelligence OS</span>
        <span class="sh-roadmap-sub">The full system — frameworks, tools and workflows in one place</span>
      </a>
      <div class="sh-roadmap-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</div>

      <a href="/applications" class="sh-roadmap-node">
        <span class="sh-roadmap-label">Applications</span>
        <span class="sh-roadmap-sub">Practical implementations across roles and sectors</span>
      </a>
      <div class="sh-roadmap-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</div>

      <a href="/work" class="sh-roadmap-node sh-roadmap-node--bottom">
        <span class="sh-roadmap-label">Consulting</span>
        <span class="sh-roadmap-sub">Working directly with organisations to implement the discipline</span>
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="sh-rule container-site" />

  <!-- ── Section 5: Explore the site ── -->
  <section class="sh-section container-site">
    <p class="sh-eyebrow">Explore the site</p>
    <h2 class="sh-h2">Find what you need</h2>
    <div class="sh-explore-grid">

      <div class="sh-explore-col">
        <p class="sh-explore-heading">Learn</p>
        <ul class="sh-explore-list">
          <li><a href="/guide" class="sh-explore-link">The AI-enabled Content Writer Guide</a></li>
          <li><a href="/intelligence" class="sh-explore-link">Editorial Intelligence</a></li>
          <li><a href="/writing/what-is-editorial-intelligence" class="sh-explore-link">What is Editorial Intelligence?</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sh-explore-col">
        <p class="sh-explore-heading">Frameworks</p>
        <ul class="sh-explore-list">
          <li><a href="/frameworks/evidence-engine" class="sh-explore-link">Evidence Engine</a></li>
          <li><a href="/cycle" class="sh-explore-link">Editorial Intelligence Cycle</a></li>
          <li><a href="/frameworks/ai-search-visibility" class="sh-explore-link">AI Search Visibility</a></li>
          <li><a href="/frameworks/customer-signal-framework" class="sh-explore-link">Customer Signals</a></li>
          <li><a href="/frameworks/narrative-architecture" class="sh-explore-link">Narrative Architecture</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sh-explore-col">
        <p class="sh-explore-heading">Applications</p>
        <ul class="sh-explore-list">
          <li><a href="/frameworks/editorial-intelligence-product-management" class="sh-explore-link">Product Management</a></li>
          <li><a href="/experiments/event-intelligence" class="sh-explore-link">Event Intelligence</a></li>
          <li><a href="/work/ai-visibility-audit" class="sh-explore-link">AI Visibility Audit</a></li>
          <li><a href="/applications" class="sh-explore-link">All Applications →</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sh-explore-col">
        <p class="sh-explore-heading">Lab</p>
        <ul class="sh-explore-list">
          <li><a href="/lab" class="sh-explore-link">Editorial Intelligence Lab</a></li>
          <li><a href="/writing" class="sh-explore-link">Field Notes</a></li>
          <li><a href="/experiments" class="sh-explore-link">Experiments</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://editorialintelligence.substack.com" class="sh-explore-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Substack ↗</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="sh-rule container-site" />

  <!-- ── Section 6: EI in practice ── -->
  <section class="sh-section container-site">
    <p class="sh-eyebrow">Editorial Intelligence in practice</p>
    <h2 class="sh-h2">Not theory. Evidence.</h2>
    <p class="sh-section-desc">Each of these programmes shows how scattered signals were turned into strategic positions that compound over time.</p>
    <div class="sh-practice-grid">

      <a href="/narratives/hidden-hours" class="sh-practice-card group">
        <p class="sh-practice-title">Hidden Hours</p>
        <div class="sh-practice-flow">
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Problem</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Research published once, archived immediately</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Evidence</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">1,000-respondent survey of UK accountants</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Narrative</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Compliance consuming less than half of practitioner time</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Activation</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Multiple editorial angles over months</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step sh-practice-step--outcome">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Outcome</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Research becomes ongoing editorial infrastructure</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="sh-practice-cta">Explore this narrative →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/narratives/winning-in-small" class="sh-practice-card group">
        <p class="sh-practice-title">Winning in Small</p>
        <div class="sh-practice-flow">
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Problem</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Event insight disappears after recap articles</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Evidence</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Customer stories, survey data, event conversations</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Narrative</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Small businesses winning in the spaces big players overlook</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Activation</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Synthesised into a single strategic argument</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step sh-practice-step--outcome">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Outcome</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Scattered evidence becomes a coherent brand position</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="sh-practice-cta">Explore this narrative →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/narratives/trusted-ai" class="sh-practice-card group">
        <p class="sh-practice-title">Trusted AI</p>
        <div class="sh-practice-flow">
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Problem</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">AI conversation dominated by fear, not practical evidence</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Evidence</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Customer insight, product signals, market research</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Narrative</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">AI as practical productivity tool, not replacement threat</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Activation</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Thought leadership, case studies, event content</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step sh-practice-step--outcome">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Outcome</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Credible, distinctive AI position built over time</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="sh-practice-cta">Explore this narrative →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/work/ai-visibility-audit" class="sh-practice-card group">
        <p class="sh-practice-title">AI Visibility</p>
        <div class="sh-practice-flow">
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Problem</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">AI systems can't find or trust your organisation's expertise</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Evidence</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Structured audit across six visibility dimensions</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Narrative</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">What you are credible about and what is limiting authority</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Activation</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Prioritised roadmap for improving AI visibility</span>
          </div>
          <span class="sh-practice-step-arrow">↓</span>
          <div class="sh-practice-step sh-practice-step--outcome">
            <span class="sh-practice-step-label">Outcome</span>
            <span class="sh-practice-step-text">Better AI representation and reduced competitor authority gaps</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="sh-practice-cta">Explore the audit →</span>
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="sh-rule container-site" />

  <!-- ── Section 7: Ready to start ── -->
  <section class="sh-section container-site">
    <p class="sh-eyebrow">Ready to start?</p>
    <h2 class="sh-h2">Choose how you want to begin</h2>
    <div class="sh-cta-grid">

      <a href="/guide" class="sh-cta-card">
        <span class="sh-cta-label">Learn</span>
        <p class="sh-cta-title">Read the Guide</p>
        <p class="sh-cta-desc">The AI-enabled Content Writer Guide — how experienced writers become Editorial Intelligence practitioners.</p>
        <span class="sh-cta-link">Start reading →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/assessment" class="sh-cta-card sh-cta-card--accent">
        <span class="sh-cta-label">Assess</span>
        <p class="sh-cta-title">Take the Assessment</p>
        <p class="sh-cta-desc">Diagnose your organisation's Editorial Intelligence maturity across five dimensions. Takes around 5 minutes.</p>
        <span class="sh-cta-link">Begin the assessment →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/work/ai-visibility-audit" class="sh-cta-card">
        <span class="sh-cta-label">Implement</span>
        <p class="sh-cta-title">Book an AI Visibility Audit</p>
        <p class="sh-cta-desc">Understand how AI systems describe your organisation and what is limiting your authority.</p>
        <span class="sh-cta-link">Explore the audit →</span>
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Footer statement ── -->
  <div class="sh-footer-statement container-site">
    <p>Editorial Intelligence isn't simply a framework.</p>
    <p>It's a way of helping organisations understand, connect and compound what they already know.</p>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Hero ── */
  .sh-hero {
    padding-top: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    padding-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);
  }

  .sh-hero-inner {
    max-width: 52rem;
  }

  .sh-time-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 35%, transparent);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .sh-h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .sh-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-ink-secondary);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .sh-support {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-ink-tertiary);
    max-width: 64ch;
  }

  /* ── Shared section ── */
  .sh-rule {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .sh-section {
    padding: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem) 0;
  }

  .sh-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .sh-h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .sh-section-desc {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-ink-secondary);
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* ── Path cards ── */
  .sh-path-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .sh-path-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }

  .sh-path-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--color-surface-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .sh-path-card:hover {
    background: var(--color-surface-tertiary);
  }

  .sh-path-icon {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .sh-path-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .sh-path-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-ink-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .sh-path-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .sh-path-cta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .sh-path-link {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-tertiary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .sh-path-link:hover { color: var(--color-ink); }

  /* ── What is EI ── */
  .sh-what-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .sh-what-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr; }
  }

  .sh-what-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .sh-what-body p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-ink-secondary);
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .sh-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.375rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 40%, transparent);
    padding: 0.6rem 1.125rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }

  .sh-btn:hover {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 8%, transparent);
  }

  .sh-what-stat-col {
